Thanks for the info.

I've just been playing with the tool, and had a few problems around setting
attributes to Real values via the GUI (the odd crash etc.). I've got it to work
now, but only by editing the .cmd file directly. Also, with inheritance the GUI
doesn't seem to notice associations to parents when creating links.

Attached are the two files I have been using.

